    <p>Use the secure link below to sign in to the Fund Forge admin panel. This link expires in 15 minutes and can only be used once.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="<%= @login_link %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 18px; background: #047881; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px;">
